title: Week 2 Rankings 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp each give their 5 most difficult players to rank for Week 2, including some players who people should not write off just yet. Plus, Liz Loza joins to help preview Bears-Packers and make a bet with Kyle.
